1.By ID(#Id)
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("#username"));

2.By Class (.input-field)

driver.findElement(By.cssSelector(".input-field"));

3. Tag + Class
button.btn
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("button.btn")).click();

4.4. Attribute
input[name='user_name']
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("input[name='user_name']")).sendKeys("test");

5.5. Contains (Partial Match)
input[name*='user']
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("input[name*='user']"));

6. Starts With
input[name^='user']
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("input[name^='user']"));

7. Ends With
input[name$='name']
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("input[name$='name']"));

8. Parent → Child
CSS
div > input
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("div > input"));

9. Ancestor → Descendant
CSS
div input
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("div input"));

10. nth-child
CSS
ul li:nth-child(2)
Selenium
driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("ul li:nth-child(2)")).click();

